{
  "stem": "23742.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And some of them wore decent clothing and looked in a much better condition than the others that we had seen.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we spent that night living in our trucks, awaiting instructions.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then, the following day we were told that we would be taking some of the prisoners back to Brussels.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We tried to make our trucks, which were not designed to carry passengers-- we tried to make it as comfortable as we could for them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We got hold of some sacking and some boxes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we made some kind of seating arrangement.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then we-- the, these prisoners were brought forward.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were each given papers of the 20 or so women.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were only-- they were all women, young women and older women.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there were 20 women on my truck.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we were given the papers of each one of them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And as I was shuffling through the papers, I noticed one of the names of the women there was named Sophie, which was my mother's name.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I sort of attached myself to this young woman.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I told her I'd look after her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But didn't mean to say I didn't look after all the others, but this one in particular.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We had rations for our journey back to-- we took water aboard.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And on the journey back, we were, we were told that we were to drive into Brussels and go straight to the [INAUDIBLE], which is the Grand Place, which is just a square outside the north station.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I was unable to converse with this young woman, because we had a language problem.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "My Yiddish wasn't all that wonderful.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
